<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

		<meta name="description" content="Explore a diverse collection of my work in web development, showcasing responsive designs, interactive projects, and innovative solutions. Get inspired by my portfolio and discover how I can bring your ideas to life.">

		<title>
